name: I Will Find Them Quickly, Master
Lore: 'Utilizing his ''dark eye'' probe droids and sensory equipment, Maul knew he would eventually find his target.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Opponent may deploy Amidala from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If Maul present with Amidala and opponent has no Jedi here, she is captured. Once per game may take If The Trace Was Correct into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
